<% layout("./layouts/boilerplate") %>

<div class="row">
  <div class="home col-10 offset-1">
    <div class="box mt-4">
      <h2 class="home-banner-name"><b>Wanderplaces</b></h2>
      <form action="/listings" method="GET">
        <button class="btn btn-dark home-btn mt-4">Explore Places</button>
      </form>
      <div class="slogan mt-4">
        <p><b>Your Journey, Our Guide,</b></p>
        <p><b>Explore More, Worry Less.</b></p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="description col-10 offset-1">
    <div class="des-title">
      <h5>Discover Us</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="description-text">
      <p>
        Discover a world of destinations with WanderPlaces, your ultimate travel
        companion. We provide detailed information, insider tips, and curated
        lists of must-see attractions and activities for each location. Whether
        you're planning your next vacation or just dreaming of future
        adventures, let WanderPlaces inspire your journey and turn your travel
        dreams into reality.
      </p>
      <img
        class="show-img col-8 offset-2 mt-2 mb-2"
        src="/images/poster1.jpg"
        alt="" />
      <p>
        Our platform is designed to cater to all types of travelers, from
        adventure seekers and culture enthusiasts to those looking for a
        relaxing getaway. We offer insights into the best local eateries, hidden
        gems, popular landmarks, and seasonal events to ensure you make the most
        of your trip.
      </p>
      <p>
        With WanderPlaces, you can explore diverse landscapes, from majestic
        mountains and serene rivers to vibrant cities and tranquil beaches. Our
        mission is to provide you with the resources and inspiration to discover
        new places, experience unique cultures, and create lasting memories.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="details col-10 offset-1 mb-4">
    <div class="des-title">
      <h5>Why Choose WanderPlaces?</h5>
    </div>
    <div class="description-text">
      <p>
        At WanderPlaces, we believe that travel should be accessible and
        enjoyable for everyone. Our user-friendly interface allows you to
        effortlessly browse through destinations, read reviews, and plan your
        itinerary. We regularly update our content to ensure you have the latest
        information at your fingertips.
      </p>
      <img
        src="/images/poster2.png"
        class="show-img col-8 offset-2 mt-2 mb-2"
        alt="" />
      <p>
        Join our community of travelers and share your own experiences, tips,
        and photos. By contributing to WanderPlaces, you help fellow travelers
        discover the best the world has to offer. Follow us on social media to
        stay updated on new destinations, travel deals, and exclusive content.
      </p>
      <p>
        Ready to start your journey? Explore our website, choose your next
        destination, and let WanderPlaces guide you every step of the way.
        Adventure awaits!
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
